We introduced Panicoid Phenomap-1 dataset in [1]. The dataset consists of images of the 40 genotypes of panicoid grain crops including at least one representative accession from each of the five categories: maize, sorghum, pearl millet, proso millet and foxtail millet. The images were captured daily by the visible light camera for two side view angles, i.e., 0\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
